  "texts": [
    "The results demonstrate the utility of machine learning in predicting employee health and well-being outcomes.",
    "By using the Random Forest algorithm, organizations can deploy predictive analytics to design proactive and personalized wellness strategies.",
    "For instance, employees predicted to have high stress levels can be offered stress management workshops or flexible working arrangements.",
    "However, it is essential to address ethical considerations, such as data privacy and ensuring that predictions are used constructively.",
    "Continuous monitoring and retraining of the model ensure its relevance as organizational dynamics and employee behaviors evolve."
